---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section id="contact" class="reveal border-t border-slate-800 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-400">
      Contacto
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
      ¿Tienes una idea, proyecto u oportunidad?
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-400">
      Estoy abierto a conversar sobre proyectos, colaboraciones y oportunidades
      relacionadas con desarrollo backend, APIs, bases de datos y sistemas web.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <a
        href="mailto:kendallchacon4@gmail.com"
        class="btn-primary-animated inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cyan-400 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-cyan-300"
      >
        Enviarme un correo
      </a>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 text-sm text-slate-400"
    >
      <a
        href="https://github.com/kendallchacon"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 transition hover:text-cyan-400"
      >
        <Icon name="simple-icons:github" class="size-5" />
        <span>GitHub</span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kendall-chacon-molina-884b04307"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 transition hover:text-cyan-400"
      >
        <Icon name="simple-icons:linkedin" class="size-5 text-blue-400" />
        <span>LinkedIn</span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="mailto:kendallchacon4@gmail.com"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 transition hover:text-cyan-400"
      >
        <Icon name="simple-icons:gmail" class="size-5 text-red-400" />
        <span>Email</span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://wa.me/50662712021"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 transition hover:text-cyan-400"
      >
        <Icon name="simple-icons:whatsapp" class="size-5 text-green-400" />
        <span>WhatsApp</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
